[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":237},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fpwa\u002F20191126\u002F3955439291\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fpwa\u002F20191126\u002F3955439291\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fpwa\u002F20191126\u002F3955439291\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fpwa\u002F20191126\u002F3955439291\u002F":218,"related:\u002Fpwa\u002F20191126\u002F3955439291\u002F":227},"\u002Fen\u002Fpwa\u002F2019\u002F11\u002F26\u002Fpwa-dev-environment-day5\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":85,"date":204,"description":18,"extension":205,"lang":206,"meta":207,"navigation":208,"path":209,"readingMinutes":210,"seo":211,"standalone":212,"stem":213,"tags":214,"tldr":215,"updated":215,"url":216,"__hash__":217},"content\u002FPWA 初體驗\u002FDay5-PWA-初體驗-PWA-開發環境.md","Day5-PWA 初體驗 - 開發環境","3955439291",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":190},"minimark",[11,15,19,22,25,35,39,47,53,60,66,69,73,81,87,90,96,99,105,109,112,118,122,125,131,134,160,163,167,170,175,178,181],[12,13,14],"h2",{"id":14},"前言",[16,17,18],"p",{},"前面講那麼多東西，也認識了基本的 PWA 架構，接下來就要來準備一下開發環境了。",[12,20,21],{"id":21},"開發環境",[16,23,24],{},"工欲善必先利其器，在開發 PWA 之前我們必須先準備好開發環境，PWA 開發環境最主要是使用 Chrome 來開發，接下來往下實作請具備好以下條件",[26,27,28,32],"ul",{},[29,30,31],"li",{},"Chrome（74或更高版本以上）。",[29,33,34],{},"懂基本的 HTML、CSS、JavaScript 以及知道 Chrome DevTools。",[12,36,38],{"id":37},"開啟-chrome-pwa-開發模式","開啟 Chrome PWA 開發模式",[16,40,41,42,46],{},"那由於 PWA 模擬環境必須手動開啟，所以這邊首先在 Chrome Url 輸入 ",[43,44,45],"code",{},"chrome:\u002F\u002Fflags\u002F"," ↓",[16,48,49],{},[50,51],"img",{"alt":45,"src":52},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FWyPv7Wn.png",[16,54,55,56,59],{},"接下來找到 ",[43,57,58],{},"Desktop PWAs local updating","，將 Default 改 Enabled ↓",[16,61,62],{},[50,63],{"alt":64,"src":65},"Enabled","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FWliug1Z.png",[16,67,68],{},"接下來只需要重新啟動 Chrome 即可。",[12,70,72],{"id":71},"驗證-pwa-開啟","驗證 PWA 開啟",[16,74,75,76,80],{},"那該如何驗證自己 PWA 已經開啟了呢?直接進入 ",[50,77],{"alt":78,"src":79},"Google I\u002FO 2016","https:\u002F\u002Fevents.google.com\u002Fio2016\u002F"," 官方網站，然後就可以在右上角安裝 PWA 囉 ↓",[16,82,83],{},[50,84],{"alt":85,"src":86},"PWA","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FmbSnSSd.png",[16,88,89],{},"安裝之後就會自動開啟 PWA 模式 ↓",[16,91,92],{},[50,93],{"alt":94,"src":95},"PWA 模式","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FHMs2IHl.png",[16,97,98],{},"接下來你可以在該 PWA 畫面下按下 F12 開啟 DevTools ↓",[16,100,101],{},[50,102],{"alt":103,"src":104},"DevTools","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002Fye2Xsv4.png",[12,106,108],{"id":107},"查看-manifest-與-service-workers","查看 manifest 與 Service Workers",[16,110,111],{},"前面兩篇都在介紹 manifest 與 Service Workers，所以這一篇當然要介紹一下該如何看 manifest 與 Service Workers，首先先開啟 DevTools，然後點 Application，接下來旁邊就可以看到 manifest 與 Service Workers 囉 ↓",[16,113,114],{},[50,115],{"alt":116,"src":117},"Application","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FsEwkNtc.png",[119,120,121],"h3",{"id":121},"manifest",[16,123,124],{},"前面我們有講到 manifest.js 就是管理一些應用程式名稱、應用程式圖案等等的 JSON 檔案，所以我們可以在這裡看到各種相關欄位設置 ↓",[16,126,127],{},[50,128],{"alt":129,"src":130},"manifest.js","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FX0DnKee.png",[16,132,133],{},"通常來講 icon 會建議放多種版本的大小，可是這部分我沒有特別研究，所以可以參考 Google 官方的 icon 大小。",[26,135,136,139,142,145,148,151,154,157],{},[29,137,138],{},"48x48",[29,140,141],{},"72x72",[29,143,144],{},"96x96",[29,146,147],{},"144x144",[29,149,150],{},"168x168",[29,152,153],{},"192x192",[29,155,156],{},"256x256",[29,158,159],{},"512x512",[16,161,162],{},"(但是這邊我實際應用僅會用 192x192 以及 512x512 的尺寸)",[119,164,166],{"id":165},"service-workers","Service Workers",[16,168,169],{},"那 Service Workers 呢?基本上會集中在這區塊 ↓",[16,171,172],{},[50,173],{"alt":166,"src":174},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FygYBFUM.png",[16,176,177],{},"但是這邊我個人覺得在實作的時候再來講會比較清楚，因為這邊只是一些基本的開發環境操作觀看而已，所以在這邊就稍微了解東西在哪裡就好。",[12,179,180],{"id":180},"參考文獻",[16,182,183],{},[184,185,189],"a",{"href":186,"rel":187},"https:\u002F\u002Fdevelopers.google.com\u002Fweb\u002Ffundamentals\u002Fcodelabs\u002Fyour-first-pwapp",[188],"nofollow","你的首個 Progressive Web App",{"title":191,"searchDepth":192,"depth":192,"links":193},"",2,[194,195,196,197,198,203],{"id":14,"depth":192,"text":14},{"id":21,"depth":192,"text":21},{"id":37,"depth":192,"text":38},{"id":71,"depth":192,"text":72},{"id":107,"depth":192,"text":108,"children":199},[200,202],{"id":121,"depth":201,"text":121},3,{"id":165,"depth":201,"text":166},{"id":180,"depth":192,"text":180},"2019-11-26 09:24:48","md","zh-Hant",{},true,"\u002Fpwa\u002Fday5-pwa-pwa","2",{"title":6,"description":18},false,"PWA 初體驗\u002FDay5-PWA-初體驗-PWA-開發環境",[85],null,"\u002Fpwa\u002F20191126\u002F3955439291\u002F","F8EIcG9OrB_RvPGBE63qlGKG7yltIJ3xwt8tFC2HEEw",{"newer":219,"older":223},{"url":220,"title":221,"date":222},"\u002Fpwa\u002F20191203\u002F2841782636\u002F","Day6-PWA 初體驗 - 小試身手","2019-12-03 09:53:48",{"url":224,"title":225,"date":226},"\u002Fjavascript\u002F20191119\u002F2727084611\u002F","有點長的淺談 JavaScript function 函式","2019-11-19 21:11:19",[228,229,233],{"url":220,"title":221,"date":222,"readingMinutes":210},{"url":230,"title":231,"date":232,"readingMinutes":210},"\u002Fpwa\u002F20191114\u002F405525681\u002F","Day4-PWA 初體驗 - PWA 架構(二)","2019-11-14 22:56:48",{"url":234,"title":235,"date":236,"readingMinutes":210},"\u002Fpwa\u002F20191104\u002F3071954899\u002F","Day3-PWA 初體驗 - PWA 架構(一)","2019-11-04 17:24:48",1784013096241]